{
  "text": "In addition, La torre et al. noted that the placentas of fetuses with CMV disease were significantly thicker than those free from disease and hence, suggested that CMV infection causes extensive placental inflammation [CITATION_1] . This may be another clue to the diagnosis but was absent in our case.",
